            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "A centralized operation management and control method for an alternating-current and direct-current hybrid system containing renewable energy/hydrogen energy comprises the following steps that S1, a large signal model of the system is expressed to obtain system coefficient matrixes A and B, X is a state variable matrix of the system, and u is a system control rate; S2, a Lyapunov function is constructed, and a new system control rate is designed as follows: unew =-kBTP [delta] X; S3, a new system model is constructed, wherein a centralized operation control framework is provided for an alternating-current and direct-current hybrid system containing renewable energy sources/hydrogen energy; S4, a power instruction of each control object is obtained; and S5, each power instruction istransmitted to each corresponding control object by the information network, and centralized operation management and control of the alternating-current and direct-current hybrid system containing renewable energy sources/hydrogen energy is realized. According to the invention, the problems of a complex controller design and a difficult parameter design in the alternating-current and direct-current hybrid system in the traditional method are reduced, and the operation performance of the renewable energy/hydrogen energy alternating-current and direct-current hybrid system is improved."
                },
                {
                    "p": "一种含可再生能源/氢能的交直流混联系统集中式运行管控方法，所述方法包括以下步骤：S1：将系统的大信号模型表示为，获取系统系数矩阵A和B，其中X为系统的状态变量矩阵，u为系统控制率；S2：构建李雅普诺夫函数，设计新的系统控制率表示为：unew=‑kBTPΔX；3：构建新的系统模型:，为含可再生能源/氢能的交直流混联系统提供了集中式运行管控的控制架构；S4：利用，获得各控制对象的功率指令；S5：信息网络将各功率指令传输至对应的各控制对象，实现含可再生能源/氢能的交直流混联系统的集中式运行管控。本发明降低了传统方法在交直流混联系统中控制器设计复杂，参数设计困难的问题，提升了可再生能源/氢能的交直流混联系统的运行性能。"
                }
            ]
